data.description:
Beautiful two-story home is spacious and inviting residence that offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Located with walking distance from Dr. Sue Shook Elementary, this home is ideal for a family seeking a tranquil yet active lifestyle. The ground floor features an open floorplan, half bathroom, hall laundry, washer and dryer stay, kitchen with ample cabinets space and breakfast bar, living room, Refrigerator, stove, microwave, will stay. Outdoor living has Covered Patio and established landscape with trees, plants and flowers for your enjoyment. Upgraded Central A/C - Newer furnace and newer roof. upstairs. Master bedroom with a walking closet and double vanity, 3 more bedrooms with a full bathroom. a bedrooms 2 full baths and one-half bath., 2 car garage, laundry on the first floor, formal dining and breakfast area, living with
fireplace, front and back yard with trees, plants and flowers, large cover patio for cook outs, shed s upstairs is the Master with walking closet and 3 more bedrooms
